title: The Only Way Is Essex Season 10
description:
The tenth series of the British semi-reality television programme The Only Way Is Essex began on 6 October 2013 with two The Only Way Is Vegas specials and was followed by a regular run of the series from 13 October 2013 until 13 November 2013.

 Jess Wright
